Package org.neo4j.consistency.checking.full

Class StoreProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.store.RecordStore.Processor<RuntimeException>
      • org.neo4j.consistency.checking.AbstractStoreProcessor
        • org.neo4j.consistency.checking.full.StoreProcessor
  • public class StoreProcessor
extends AbstractStoreProcessor
    Full check works by spawning StoreProcessorTasks that call StoreProcessor. StoreProcessor.applyFiltered() then scans the store and in turn calls down to store.accept which then knows how to check the given record.
